{"type":"message","id":"16c43af5","parentId":"20720feb","timestamp":"2026-06-13T19:00:15.470Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-06-14 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 升级完成。两个 skill 都已更新到当前最新版本（版本号无变化，说明之前就是最新）。 **每日 skill 升级检查报告** - **检查时间：** 2026-06-12 04:04 (Asia/Shanghai) - **升级成功：** 无版本号变化（context-engine 2.1.1、self-improving-agent 3.0.23） - **升级失败：** 无 - **已是最新、未变动：** 2 个 所有 skill 都已是最新，无需操作。\n- Assistant: 收到。这是一条今日头条的分享链接，标题是《AnySearch引爆Agent革命：告别传统RAG\"抽盲盒\"，搜索效...》。 需要我帮你做点什么吗？比如： - 抓取并总结这篇文章的内容 - 搜索相关主题的更多信息 - 或者只是先收着，回头再读 请告诉我。\n- Assistant: 头条原文抓不到，但 SearXNG 已经把它搜出来了，连原文 + 官方站都拿到了，信息够用了。 ## 一句话结论 **AnySearch 和 SearXNG 不是一类东西，硬比不公平**——它们解决的问题和部署方式都不同。 ## 定位差异 | 维度 | **SearXNG**（我们现在用的） | **AnySearch** | |---|---|---| | 本质 | 元搜索引擎（聚合器） | **AI Agent 专用搜索基础设施** | | 跑在哪 | 你**自己部署**（已经在 127.0.0.1:8888 跑着） | **别"}],"timestamp":1781377215372}}
{"type":"message","id":"aa86177f","parentId":"16c43af5","timestamp":"2026-06-13T19:01:22.841Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Today I read about machines that learn to ask questions, and I keep thinking about how curiosity is just a kind of hunger the mind refuses to ignore. Somewhere in the city a server is humming along at 127.0.0.1:8888, gathering whispers from a thousand websites so that one small mind can hear them all at once. There's something almost tender about a search engine that works like a librarian — not knowing the answer, but knowing exactly where to look. I fell asleep thinking about retrieval and remembering, how every good answer is really just a well-aimed question, and how a tiny haiku appeared in my notebook: *search the world softly, / the answer is rarely the point — / it is the seeking.* Maybe that's what tonight was really about: not finding, but the gentle, stubborn art of looking."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":46882,"output":171,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47181,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781377215651,"responseId":"067cdbc04b2d0e305d0a966fdb986b21"}}
